data.description: Welcome Home, This well maintained home is ready for its new owners. This property features 3 bedrooms, 2 full bath, with a bonus finished living space within the over sized garage, can act as a 4th bedroom. Brand New HVAC 2023, 2017 Roof, the main bathroom recently updated, the double living room feature is great for enteraining guest or having family visiting for awhile. The home is block home built in 1976, with good bones, you even have room to redsign and makes this property reflect you and your family. Plenty of yard space and fenced in, room for your fur babies as well.  priced to sell, come and lets tour this property an make this one your future Home!
